==============================================================================
                     R E Q U I R E D   L I B R A R I E S
==============================================================================

MANDATORY:

   - libpcap >= 0.8.1
   - libnet  >= 1.1.1
   - libpthread

OPTIONAL:

   - libltdl (part of libtool)   (for the plugin support)
   - libpcre                     (for perl regexp in the filters)
   - zlib                        (for compressed log files)
   - openssl                     (for ssh and ssl support)
   - ncurses                     (for the curses GUI)




